# 2Ô∏è‚É£1Ô∏è‚É£ RELATIONSHIP TO OTHER LOGICS

* Logic 1 ‚Üí Verifies identity of approvers
* Logic 2 ‚Üí Defines role-based authority
* Logic 3 ‚Üí Approves procurement need
* Logic 8 ‚Üí Approves evaluation outcome
* Logic 9 ‚Üí Uses price risk in escalation
* Logic 10 ‚Üí Approves award & contract

It acts as the **control backbone of the entire procurement system**.

